    "body": "<p>This issue sounds a lot like my issue on dotnet/aspnetcore: <a href=\"https://github.com/dotnet/aspnetcore/issues/23606\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">WebAssembly.Authentication - Not possible to define &quot;Audience&quot;</a></p>\n<p>I solved this by creating a new <strong>Auth0ProviderOptions</strong> which extends from the <strong>OidcProviderOptions</strong> and defining <code>extraQueryParams</code>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>See <a href=\"https://github.com/StefH/Blazor.WebAssembly.Authentication.Auth0/blob/master/src/Blazor.WebAssembly.Authentication.Auth0/Auth0ProviderOptions.cs\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">this link for the class</a></li>\n<li>See <a href=\"https://github.com/StefH/Blazor.WebAssembly.Authentication.Auth0\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">this link for the complete example project</a></li>\n</ul>\n"
